# Application Blueprint

When generating or refactoring, preserve this architecture:

- Next.js App Router in `src/app` with domain route groups (`(_home)`, `(classes)`, `(students)`, `(appointments)`, etc.)
- Domain-local `_actions`, `_components`, and `_context` where needed
- Prisma + PostgreSQL: `prisma/schema.prisma`, config in `prisma.config.ts`, seeds under `prisma/seeds/**`, entry `prisma/seed.ts`
- Prisma client singleton: `src/lib/prisma.ts`
- JWT cookie sessions and helpers: `src/app/lib/session.ts`
- Shared domain types and Zod form contracts: `src/app/lib/definitions.ts`; pure grading/behavior helpers: `src/app/lib/grading.ts`; formatting: `src/app/lib/typeConversion.ts` when used
- Fonts: `src/app/lib/fonts.ts`; global CSS: `src/app/globals.css`; root shell: `src/app/layout.tsx`
- Global modals: `ModalProvider` + `<Modal />` in root `layout.tsx`, context in `src/app/(_home)/_context/Modal.tsx`, triggers in `src/app/(_home)/_components/OpenModalComponents/**`

## Implementation order (high level)

1. **Bootstrap** — dependencies and tooling (`.cursor/rules/setup/install-dependencies.mdc`; full sequence `.cursor/skills/bootstrap-dependencies/SKILL.md`).
2. **Directories** — route groups, `_actions`, `_components`, shared `src/lib` and `src/app/lib` (see `.cursor/rules/frontend/directory-organization.mdc`).
3. **Database** — schema, migrations, seeds (`.cursor/rules/database/database-setup.mdc`; commands `.cursor/skills/prisma-database-workflow/SKILL.md`).
4. **Authentication** — session payload, cookie helpers, signup/login/logout actions (`.cursor/rules/authentication/authentication-setup.mdc`; workflow `.cursor/skills/implement-authentication-flow/SKILL.md`).
5. **Root layout** — metadata, viewport, fonts on `<body>`, global providers (see `.cursor/rules/frontend/layout-structure.mdc`).
6. **Server actions** — per-domain `_actions` files, validation, revalidation (see `.cursor/rules/frontend/server-action-structure-organization.mdc`).
7. **Pages and feature components** — thin `page.tsx`, feature folders with section files (`.cursor/rules/frontend/page-component-structure.mdc`). End-to-end feature work: `.cursor/skills/feature-vertical-slice/SKILL.md`.
8. **Modals** — site-wide portal pattern and colocated `Modals/` trees (`.cursor/rules/frontend/modal-setup-structure.mdc`; add modal `.cursor/skills/add-feature-modal/SKILL.md`).
9. **CSS and Tailwind** — tokens in `globals.css`, theme usage in components (`.cursor/rules/frontend/css-setup-structure.mdc`; extend tokens `.cursor/skills/extend-design-tokens/SKILL.md`).
10. **Shared types and helpers** — extend definitions and lib modules as domains grow (see `.cursor/rules/frontend/type-and-domain-lib-organization.mdc`).

